data.text: I had the honor today to put on my Army dress uniform once again after more than a decade to retire LTC Rosalyn "Sherie" King. Sherie and her husband John have had such an impact on so many soldiers throughout their military career and I was one of them. She has always been an inspiration with such moral courage while holding herself and her soldiers to the highest standards. She has already taken her first step into industry at Cisco as part of their Career Skills Program for transitioning Veterans. She once again has such a bright future ahead and I cannot wait to see her blaze this next trail. Please welcome her with open arms as the transition can be daunting but if anyone can conquer it is Sherie! Rosalyn "Sherie" King John King James McGruder
